</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>The letter-book copy is corrected to read the 19th.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>For Congresss formal letter of congratulations on the evacuation of Boston, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-04-02-0016" class="document">Hancock to GW, 2 April 1776</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>Congress passed this resolution on 21 Mar. 1776 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington Chauncey Ford et al., eds. &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 1774-1789&lt;/i&gt;. 34 vols. Washington, D.C., 190437. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 4:223).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0397-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>For this resolution of 25 Mar., see ibid., 236.</p>

</div>
